COPY_EXISTING ~book10.itm~ ~override/c0sbook3.itm~
SAY NAME1 ~Zalorne's Journal~
SAY NAME2 ~Zalorne's Journal~
SAY DESC ~The first several pages of this journal contain very little interest, save for a few entries which mostly consist of insults towards several named members of the Arcane Brotherhood of Luskan. The profanities written in the journal include those from the Common tongue, words borrowed from at least three foreign languages and several which sound made up. Only the most recent entries hold anything of value.

"Kythorn 2
One of the mercenaries drank too much again and vomited all over my favorite robes. The pig! He has been punished with permanent lobotomy via a Feeblemind spell and left on the wayside to rot. Bah! I shall have to wear the one I brought from the Hosttower. That one, at least, is enchanted to remove stains."

"Kythorn 4
A man in rags passed by our regular raiding path today. We allowed him to pass. It was clear that he had nothing of value."

"Kythorn 5
Interesting. The man from yesterday has returned, and visited the ruined chapel in the nearby village. That place has been abandoned since the recent Bhaalspawn wars. What could he be doing?"

"Kythorn 7
There is an altar within the chapel, but some enchantment prevents anyone from entering the grounds. Blast! I must know what has been hidden in those ruins. Perhaps it is an artifact powerful enough to help me reclaim my position at the Hosttower."

"Kythorn 9
Two days spent attempting to break the glyphs surrounding those ruins with no luck. This is pointless. I shall have to wait and observe from the shadows. Someone will come for it... eventually."~

